Casablanca,ED3l5fWzFio,Ugy-ocqgXzku6r6JFWt4AaABAg,,@kimberlykasimoff1447,"I don't care for the modern day documentaries of the wonderful old films.  I have watched documentaries from years back that included people who had actually worked on and in the films.  I used to do film research, but on the old films.  I even did a lot of the  research for a book titled Final Curtain.  There were two books written at the same time with the same title about where actresses and actors were buried and a bit of information about each person.  Margaret Burke, who used to have the monthly meetings at I think The Beverly Hills Hotel with recent writers of books about themselves and say, the daughter of Sammy Davis Jr., hired me to research where the people who she had included in the book were buried and how they had died.  I actually had to ask her about listing those who had helped her on the book.  Yes, I wanted to see my name there.  I also worked with my husband who worked for NHK Japan as a video cameraman when they needed research for their documentaries.",2025-07-23T05:25:32Z,2025-07-23T05:25:32Z,0,False,0.0,2026-05-20T02:01:13.824808
