Marrakech,05QDGvi0_sM,UgwbE-5lOknjDGGsH0Z4AaABAg,,@5217tuber,"My wife and I enjoyed this video, having taken a package tour of Morocco in 2022 that included about 4 days in Marrakech.  My only comment is that we made a non-tour stop to both Jardin Majorelle and Yves Saint Laurent’s museum (both very near to each other) and found each of them worthwhile.  I wanted to experience YSL mainly for its modern architecture but the exhibition they had was very good as well.  I will add that by the time we’d been in Morocco for 3 weeks, I was tired of Tagine dinners (but liked the kefta option, like Kevin).",2024-11-03T00:35:41Z,2024-11-03T00:35:41Z,15,False,1.0,2026-05-20T02:01:46.262774
