Tangier,bpKJSB4HUfE,Ughv_ITTXPrsZHgCoAEC,,@SueHutton,"I see this was made in 2010. Many big changes in Tangier road systems since then and there is a project to 'join up' Tangier and Malabata bays. The view will be amazing as cruise liners come into port. If anyone is up, that is. They tend to come in before dawn. The medina is just the same. Oh, and the clubs and bars along the corniche have all been demolished for a vision of a 'clean' Tangier which is family friendly. That area will also look on to a marina. The fishing port is being shunted sideways. They're supposed to be trying to keep the walls of the Kasbah but they look very precarious.",2016-10-18T14:23:58Z,2016-10-18T14:23:58Z,1,False,0.0,2026-05-20T02:02:11.921079
