Tourism,wFZyNQAIcdE,UgwALF8-nhMuMfg3ruh4AaABAg,,@msmargiek48,"I just got back from Bali and we loved it. Sure some traffic but not like you said we got around just fine. Hawaii, went in the 80's and it was wonderful, now, it's a all around tourist trap from, Oahu, to Maui to Kona., be been last year and never again. So many other great beach places like Bali, I would travel farther to be treated better. Been to Santorini and loved that too, went on should season and it was beautiful. Mount Rushmore was great, I dont understand that one. I love to travel and been to most of these and I guess I just appreciate things as they come and not so critical.",2026-05-06T03:03:35Z,2026-05-06T03:03:35Z,0,False,0.0,2026-05-20T02:02:42.363022
