Tourism,Rl_YSqygFEM,UgwroGXo_Bti07-AVqZ4AaABAg.AIn4B17nWIrATg612-J8AF,UgwroGXo_Bti07-AVqZ4AaABAg,@mikego7325,"It's shocking, to say the least. It's been a lifelong dream of mine to visit Japan, so I empathise with both the local Japanese communities impacted by this as well as the respectful tourists whose ability to travel and appreciate Japanese culture will be undoubtedly impacted by policy changes in reaction to these issues. On balance, since the Japanese government has been encouraging tourism to bolster its economy, I believe it would be helpful for the government to publish official guidance on Japanese etiquette and norms. (Yes, it is the responsibility of each traveller to educate themselves, but it would be a proactive step.)",2026-02-26T07:17:32Z,2026-02-26T07:17:32Z,0,True,,2026-05-20T02:02:43.588970
