Tourism,Rl_YSqygFEM,UgwroGXo_Bti07-AVqZ4AaABAg.AIn4B17nWIrAWX7Q2oE4yk,UgwroGXo_Bti07-AVqZ4AaABAg,@DoinStuff4Life,As an American that bought a house in Japan but doesn't  live here full-time. And as someone who's been coming out to Japan at least once a year since 2006 this disgusts me. I don't understand how tourists feel like they can do whatever they want when they are guests in this country. Like I said I own property here and I follow the rules and regulations as if I lived here full time but with the mindset of I'm a guest here. I really don't blame the prime Minister for wanting to thin out tourism here. And making it harder for westerners to live here as much as it hurts me someone who follows the rules. I get it and I support it,2026-05-07T23:51:27Z,2026-05-07T23:52:36Z,1,True,,2026-05-20T02:02:43.588993
