It's wrong.
Those people who stole money, they are making bad example for the country and people.
It encourages bad behaviour and keeps everyone poor.
It makes foreighners look down on phillipinos.
It makes the entire phillipino community look bad and untrustworthy.
If pinoys love their country and family, they need to punish those who do scam business and lies.
Then encourage the virtue of independency, not rely on others, frugality, save money, and do honest work.
It's hard and it make take time, but do this phillipine will eventually become wealthier.

Honesty and good heart.
Do not worry about money,
Seek the kingdom of god first, then everything will be added unto you.
The lord said this and it is true.
